{"tid":1476032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班學生學乜嘢人罷課","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:50:10.000Z","uid":277873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42e5d64046338536e1dd125894aad9bce25df585","tid":1476032,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">罷乜都好，保護咗自己安全先呀！</span></span><br />\n見到有學生話發夢發到畀屋企人打同趕出街，你哋CLS架？咁都想要自己一個頂！？係咪當我哋啲大人a joke to you????<br />\n<br />\n係我係講你呀，你呢啲太直正有志氣，好純真咁唔想接受任何利益，唔想留藉口畀人攻擊你哋為理想而行動既初心......情願瞓街都好禮貌咁拒絕唔想麻煩其他人既細佬！<br />\n<br />\n唔該你哋轉轉個腦啦，唔好當其他人幫你係資助你哋去發夢，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">錯晒</span></strong>，邊個話免費架？邊個話係幫你去發夢架？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借畀你架咋！你要還架！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗱，想當年我失業窮到燶，朋友想請我食飯但我自尊心太強一口拒絕。<br />\n朋友話：你應該咁諗，你將來搵到工，去請返一個失業既朋友食餐好既，就係還咗畀我。<br />\n<br />\n真係一言驚醒洛克人！於是我好安心咁食咗佢餐飯，後來我搵到嘢做，後來我只要見到有失業既朋友就會請佢食飯。<br />\n<br />\n醒吓啦！你哋啲暫時無屋企返既學生，唔好覺得「無乜事、捱幾日或者可以返去」。我求吓你哋真係去搵社工、教會或者其他信得過既家長（&larr;驚畀人起底既真係可以試吓搵教會或者612基金之類），畀個瓦遮頭你，睇醫生，梳洗吓，安心瞓覺好既。係呀你會欠咗呢啲陌生人，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">你將來有經濟能力再還畀其他有需要既人</span></span>就得架啦！咁係<strong>幫助我哋啲大人延續條人性既連鎖建設香港</strong>，唔關你出唔出去發夢事。<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋身邊有呢啲硬頸既細佬，唔該COPY畀佢哋睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d245fdc63ab455dc4b46225cdfe3ec93dda452","tid":1476032,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"61edf640592f99f04a7af3a96349aea2478849e1","tid":1476032,"uid":273234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waFadsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaFadsG.jpg&h=75076580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83df4116acc0fc72eff212621ab6689998021522","tid":1476032,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅機會啊！８２３和理非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈</span></strong>，萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"467d411a2cacc0e7c280f19033e95762db9a9717","tid":1476032,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:21:36.000Z","msg":"P牌無得自己正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa55230888be4249ac0c164c1d97bfaa8e474e1","tid":1476032,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"607bf90251eaa4a72b00fceedf4eeea61618783b","tid":1476032,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61edf640592f99f04a7af3a96349aea2478849e1","tid":1476032,"uid":273234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waFadsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaFadsG.jpg&h=75076580&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"屋企人唔諒解真係會痛入心<br />\n我屌你林鄭破壞咗香港幾多家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d19fce499239105009412663d98f21b179a791","tid":1476032,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8bb4235aef6224c9db39